101
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,200
-Sir!
-Mr. Hwang!

102
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,360
It's that man from yesterday.

103
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,880
He was a professor?

104
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,360
What's wrong with him?

105
